OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy but dry and bright at first,
OL,7,Fwith perhaps a few brief sunny
OL,8,Fintervals. Cloud will then thicken
OL,9,Ffrom the west overnight, but
OL,10,Fconditions should remain dry.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FDry and bright at first, with
OL,13,Fcloud thickening through the morning.
OL,14,FOutbreaks of rain and showers then
OL,15,Fslowly spreading east, some perhaps on
OL,16,Fthe heavy-side early evening. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
