OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FFairly
OL,6,Fcloudy though largely dry Wednesday,
OL,7,Fsome sunshine developing later.
OL,8,FImproving after a windy start on
OL,9,FThursday, with sunny spells and
OL,10,Fperhaps the odd shower. Dry, bright
OL,11,Fand warm Friday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
